Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.95,0:20:12.90,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,不准偷窥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:15.37,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,谁稀罕偷窥你 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:18.30,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,各位久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:21.52,Default,both,0,0,0,,哎 大家都已经进去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.65,0:20:24.05,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.80,0:20:26.95,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,哇 雾气好浓呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:28.75,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,美夏 感觉怎么样呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:30.55,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,水温热不热呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.42,0:20:37.92,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,美夏 索菲 茉莉奈老师 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.00,0:20:45.07,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,没事吧…你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.07,0:20:48.05,Default,Nouet,0,0,0,,你是那个驾驶员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.32,0:20:50.57,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,你受伤了吗 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.15,0:20:52.20,Default,Nouet,0,0,0,,不要你同情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.67,0:20:54.65,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,就算你这么说也不能放着你不管啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:55.27,Default,Nouet,0,0,0,,不要管我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:57.72,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,剑之介
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.50,0:21:02.02,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.67,0:21:04.15,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,公主！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.85,0:21:05.97,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,我不是公主
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:08.82,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,雪公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.13,0:21:09.80,Default,Nouet,0,0,0,,别碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:11.35,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,我去找人来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.32,0:21:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不必担心 直升机马上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.45,0:21:17.72,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,直升机 又来？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.62,0:21:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
