Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.85,0:21:22.72,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,哦 好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.32,0:21:25.82,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,美夏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.12,0:21:46.72,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,由希奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.37,0:21:54.45,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,剑之介…！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.55,0:21:57.87,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,由希奈…！
